rows.label: tlk42410111_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Cylinders are an indispensable
item for a salvager, mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Without them, you can't salvage,
and that's a problem, mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Even within this Goldmund, the
things you can get differ depending
on where you salvage, mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Here on the Salvage Deck,
the Goldmund Flight Deck...
and the Uzushio...

rows.label: tlk42410111_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I think it's a good idea to try
salvaging in various places, mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_02_msg0006
rows.name:
But sometimes, you pull up
scary-scary monsters... mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_02_msg0007
rows.name:
That's why I'm staying put
here without salvaging... mo.
